      <summary>Perspectives</summary>
      <strong><a href="https://perspectives.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Perspectives</a> is an awe-inspiring comprehensive study course that is rooted in the Scriptures.</strong>
      <p>Over a <strong>fifteen-lesson discipleship course</strong> exploring different aspects of God’s global purpose, participants examine the story of God fulfilling His promises from four vantage points or “perspectives”: Biblical, Historical, Cultural, and Strategic.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Learn more about the <a href="https://perspectives.org/course-overview/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">course and content</a></strong>. For most people, the Certificate option will be the best.</li>
        <li><strong>Learn about <a href="https://perspectives.org/find-a-class/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">upcoming Perspectives classes online and near you</a>.</strong></li>
        <li><strong>For staff who prefer a compact class</strong> (one week with time to prepare and finish assignments), reach out to Mike (m.krajnak@ifiusa.org) or Avery (a.prevette@ifiusa.org).</li>
      </ul>
      <em><strong>God's mobilized over 250,000 alumni - including many IFI staff. How may He lead you?</strong></em>
    </details>
    <details class="rl-acc">
      <summary>Gordon Conwell</summary>
      <p><a href="https://www.gordonconwell.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Gordon Conwell Theological Seminary</a> combines a rich tradition with cutting-edge educational innovation. Rooted in the gospel and God’s Word, the seminary seeks to develop Christian leaders who are thoughtful, globally aware, spiritually mature and ready for a broad array of ministries.</p>
      <p>IFI partners with Gordon Conwell to provide staff an opportunity to gain affordable seminary education by providing staff who enroll and are accepted <strong>40% off their tuition</strong>.</p>
      <p>Learn more by checking out <a href="https://www.gordonconwell.edu/blog/scholarships/international-friendships-partnership/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">our page</a>.</p>
      <em>For more information or questions, contact <strong>Robin McIntire</strong> (rmcintire1@gordonconwell.edu)</em>
    </details>
